    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 987.2-generation Cayman S is a superlative driver\u2019s example featuring the 3.4L 9A1 flat-six engine with Direct Fuel Injection (DFI), eliminating IMS concerns. The mid-ship powerplant is paired with a short-throw 6-speed manual transaxle and an optional mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally communicative, benefiting from Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and upgraded stainless steel brake lines for improved pedal modulation. Recent preventative maintenance includes a drive belt replacement and a comprehensive walnut blasting of the intake valves to ensure optimal airflow. While showing minor cosmetic patina from spirited road use, the drivetrain exhibits zero bore scoring and pulls linearly to the 7,500 RPM redline.",
      "price": 34500.0,
